20/04/2010
SOFIA, Bulgaria -- The defence ministry and the US Embassy in Sofia announced on Monday (April 19th) the start of a 12-day joint military exercise dubbed Thracian Spring 2010.
Training is under way near the city of Plovdiv and in the Yambol region, where two US air bases are located.
(BGNES, BNR, Xinhua - 19/04/10)
